OL,7,FA primary school teacher who filmed
OL,8,Fhimself sexually abusing his pupils
OL,9,Fwill face another parole hearing,
OL,10,Fwhich will be held in public.
OL,12,FDescribed as a "predatory paedophile",
OL,13,FNigel Leat captured on camera the
OL,14,Fattacks he carried out on five young
OL,15,Fgirls over the course of five years at
OL,16,FHillside First School in Weston-super-
OL,17,FMare, Somerset.
