OL,7,FLeat, now aged 63 is also known by the
OL,8,Fsurname Russell. He was jailed
OL,9,Findefinitely in 2011 after admitting
OL,10,F36 offences including attempted rape
OL,11,Fof a child and sexual assault.
OL,13,FHe was first released from prison in
OL,14,FDecember 2020 having been found
OL,15,F"suitable for release" but was
OL,16,Frecalled to prison in March 2021 for
OL,17,Fbreaching his licence conditions.
