OL,7,FAccording to Parole Board documents he
OL,8,Fwas "accessing concerning material on
OL,9,Fthe internet linked to his continuing
OL,10,Fsexual interest in children".
OL,12,FThe Parole Board said: "Following his
OL,13,Freturn to custody, various items of
OL,14,Fconcern were found in his cell. On 7
OL,15,FFebruary 2022 a panel of the Parole
OL,16,FBoard found that Mr Leat's recall to
OL,17,Fcustody was appropriate."
OL,19,F"That panel did not direct his release
OL,20,For recommend Mr Leat for open
OL,21,Fconditions."
