OL,7,FLeat's case was again referred to the
OL,8,FParole Board in January last year and
OL,9,Fa fresh hearing has been ordered,
OL,10,Fwhich has been listed for 18 March.
OL,12,FHe objected to the hearing being held
OL,13,Fin public as it "could be detrimental
OL,14,Fto his rehabilitation" and "may result
OL,15,Fin increased risk to him" and expose
OL,16,Fhis current identity.
