OL,7,F"The stress of a public hearing may
OL,8,Fimpact on Mr Leat's health. Mr Leat
OL,9,Fwould be questioned on private matters
OL,10,Fand could not be as open in a public
OL,11,Fforum," parole poard documents state.
OL,13,F"Mr Leat is remorseful and a public
OL,14,Fhearing could impact on his victims."
OL,16,FCaroline Corby, chair of the parole
OL,17,Fboard, rejected Leat's objections and
OL,18,Fsaid that in the "interests of
OL,19,Fjustice" the "high bar" threshold had
OL,20,Fbeen met for a public hearing.
