OL,7,F"Mr Leat was in a position of trust as
OL,8,Fa teacher and his offending was
OL,9,Fextensive. It is in the interests of
OL,10,Fjustice that the public see how the
OL,11,Fboard assesses risks in a case such as
OL,12,Fthis," she said.
OL,14,F"The Parole Board has not yet held a
OL,15,Fpublic hearing for a prisoner
OL,16,Fconvicted of child sexual offences.
OL,17,FThere is increased scrutiny regarding
OL,18,Fthe safety of women and girls, which
OL,19,Fis relevant to the issues in this case.
